#. <section class="sutta" id="sn38.9"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn38.9:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 38"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 38"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn38.9:0.2"
msgid "1. Jambukhādakavagga"
msgstr "1. With Jambukhādaka"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn38.9:0.3"
msgid "9. Avijjāpañhāsutta"
msgstr "9. A Question About Ignorance"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli4.257"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn38.9:1.1"
msgid "“‘Avijjā, avijjā’ti, āvuso sāriputta, vuccati."
msgstr "“Reverend Sāriputta, they speak of this thing called ‘ignorance’."

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.2"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, āvuso, avijjā”ti?"
msgstr "What is ignorance?”"

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.3"
msgid ""
"“Yaṃ kho, āvuso, dukkhe aññāṇaṃ, dukkhasamudaye aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhe "
"aññāṇaṃ, dukkhanirodhagāminiyā paṭipadāya aññāṇaṃ—"
msgstr ""
"“Not knowing about suffering, the origin of suffering, the cessation of "
"suffering, and the practice that leads to the cessation of suffering."

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.4"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccatāvuso, avijjā”ti."
msgstr "This is called ignorance.”"

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.5"
msgid "“Atthi panāvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etissā avijjāya pahānāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""
"“But, reverend, is there a path and a practice for giving up that ignorance?”"

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.6"
msgid "“Atthi kho, āvuso, maggo atthi paṭipadā, etissā avijjāya pahānāyā”ti."
msgstr "“There is.” …"

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.7"
msgid "“Katamo panāvuso, maggo katamā paṭipadā, etissā avijjāya pahānāyā”ti?"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.8"
msgid ""
"“Ayameva kho, āvuso, ariyo aṭṭhaṅgiko maggo, etissā avijjāya pahānāya, "
"seyyathidaṃ—"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.9"
msgid "sammādiṭṭhi … pe … sammāsamādhi."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.10"
msgid "Ayaṃ kho, āvuso, maggo ayaṃ paṭipadā, etissā avijjāya pahānāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.11"
msgid "“Bhaddako, āvuso, maggo bhaddikā paṭipadā, etissā avijjāya pahānāya."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "sn38.9:1.12"
msgid "Alañca panāvuso sāriputta, appamādāyā”ti."
msgstr ""

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn38.9:1.13"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
